data.description: Welcome to 105 Julius Keller Rd., Strasburg, VA – a charming retreat on 2.19 acres. This 3-bed, 2-bath property boasts stylish luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout. Step outside to an expansive Trex Deck, perfect for relaxation and enjoying the scenic views. The partially fenced yard features a quaint pond, adding a touch of serenity. Embrace a modern lifestyle against the backdrop of nature in this inviting home, offering both comfort and tranquility. Don't miss the chance to make 105 Julius Keller Rd. your peaceful haven.
